The power of cotton is an almighty force for kids attire. Our cotton spandex interlock is a thicker fabric that's durable and naturally comfortable. Plus with breathability and slight stretch, children's tops and dresses are free-moving during play time. Choose from various designs like this dinosaur patch pattern, and you have a loving sewing project for awesome practicality and personality.
